<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <title>Install Chrome Extension</title>
</head>

<body>
  <h1>
    Install Chrome Extension
  </h1>
  <div>
    <p>✅ Chrome extension files copied.</p>
    <p>1. Open Extensions in Chrome: <a href="chrome://extensions/" target="_blank">chrome://extensions/</a></p>
    <p>2. Click "Load Unpacked" and select directory:</p>
    <pre>{{ .INSTALL_DIR }}</pre>
    <p>3. Copy the newly created extension's ID and update chrome connection with this value.</p>
    <p>4. Restart Chrome.</p>
  </div>
</body>

</html>
